chapters.title: 1. Adding more information to a story

description:
As you might have guessed, watching Tucker Carlson for a week was pretty rough. While it wasn't as painful as, say, Tim Pool, it was nonetheless a drag to have to listen to this guy spread his propaganda. That said, I did learn some stuff about how he puts his show together, and just how thick the nonsense is, so I figured I'd share.

This video covers the week of October 18, 2021. Some of the information may be out of date, but I did the best I could with what I could find at the time. If any corrections need to be made, let me know in the comments below.
